       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. TransferMoney.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  SENDER-BALANCE       PIC 9(5)V99 VALUE 0.
       01  RECEIVER-BALANCE     PIC 9(5)V99 VALUE 0.
       01  AMOUNT               PIC 9(5)V99 VALUE 0.
       01  TRANSFER-SUCCESS     PIC X(10) VALUE "NO".

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           ACCEPT SENDER-BALANCE FROM COMMAND-LINE
           ACCEPT RECEIVER-BALANCE FROM COMMAND-LINE
           ACCEPT AMOUNT FROM COMMAND-LINE.

           IF SENDER-BALANCE >= AMOUNT
               SUBTRACT AMOUNT FROM SENDER-BALANCE
               ADD AMOUNT TO RECEIVER-BALANCE
               MOVE "YES" TO TRANSFER-SUCCESS
           ELSE
               MOVE "NO" TO TRANSFER-SUCCESS
           END-IF.

           DISPLAY "TRANSFER SUCCESS: " TRANSFER-SUCCESS
           DISPLAY "SENDER NEW BALANCE: " SENDER-BALANCE
           DISPLAY "RECEIVER NEW BALANCE: " RECEIVER-BALANCE.

           STOP RUN.
